ch.epfl.sweng.smarteat.models.users

Class SmartEatUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.sweng.smarteat.models.users.DBUser
      • ch.epfl.sweng.smarteat.models.users.SmartEatUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RestaurantCache.Listener

    public final class SmartEatUser
extends DBUser
implements RestaurantCache.Listener
    Created by Adrien LAMIT on 07/10/16. For the course : Software Engineering at EPFL

    This class is a Singleton there can be only one currentUser at a time.

    Mutable class, warning when you use it !

    This class describes a SmartEatUser and all its data. It also contains methods that will make computation on the SmartEatUser instances.

    This class auto-update herself from firebase you can consider the data real-time.
